&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bandwidth&lt;/strong&gt;, a prior “Best of EC” award winner, is a global software company that helps enterprises deliver exceptional experiences through voice, messaging, and emergency services. Reaching 65+ countries and over 90 percent of the global economy, we&#39;re the only provider offering an owned communications cloud that delivers advanced automation, AI integrations, global reach, and premium human support.&amp;nbsp;Bandwidth is trusted for mission-critical communications by the Global 2000, hyperscalers, and SaaS builders!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Bandwidth, your music matters when you are part of the BAND. &amp;nbsp;We celebrate differences and encourage BANDmates to be their authentic selves. &amp;nbsp;#jointheband&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Are Looking For:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a versatile and tech-savvy AI Graphic Design Intern to join our creative team for Summer 2026. In this role, you will bridge the gap between traditional design craft and emerging AI technologies. You will assist in producing high-quality visual assets for digital, social, and print platforms, utilizing both the &lt;strong&gt;Adobe Creative Suite&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Generative AI tools&lt;/strong&gt; to accelerate workflows and push creative boundaries.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hybrid Asset Creation:&lt;/strong&gt; Design engaging visuals for social media, email, and web using a mix of traditional graphic design and AI-generated imagery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI-Enhanced Workflow:&lt;/strong&gt; Use tools like &lt;strong&gt;Adobe Firefly&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Eleven Labs&lt;/strong&gt; to rapidly prototype concepts, generate mood boards, and create custom stock assets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Refinement &amp;amp; Polishing:&lt;/strong&gt; Take raw AI outputs and professionally &quot;finish&quot; them using Photoshop (Generative Fill, retouching) and Illustrator to ensure they meet brand standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brand Consistency:&lt;/strong&gt; Apply established brand guidelines across all projects, ensuring that even AI-generated content feels cohesive and intentional.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Digital &amp;amp; Print Support:&lt;/strong&gt; Assist in the layout of internal digital promotions and traditional print collateral (flyers, signage, etc.).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborative Innovation:&lt;/strong&gt; Participate in brainstorming sessions and help the team stay updated on the latest AI design plugins and automation techniques.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Need:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education:&lt;/strong&gt; Currently pursuing a&amp;nbsp; bachelors degree in Graphic Design, Digital Media, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Core Software Proficiency:&lt;/strong&gt; Strong skills in &lt;strong&gt;Adobe Photoshop and Illustrator&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Toolset:&lt;/strong&gt; Hands-on experience with &lt;strong&gt;Generative AI platforms&lt;/strong&gt; and an understanding of effective prompt engineering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Design Fundamentals:&lt;/strong&gt; A solid grasp of typography, color theory, composition, and grid systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Adaptability:&lt;/strong&gt; A &quot;hacker&quot; mindset with the ability to learn new software and AI features as they are released.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Attention to Detail:&lt;/strong&gt; A critical eye for quality, specifically the ability to spot and fix common AI artifacts (anatomy, lighting, or text errors).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Application Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Portfolio:&lt;/strong&gt; A link to an online portfolio showcasing your design work. We are specifically interested in seeing your &lt;strong&gt;process&lt;/strong&gt;—how you’ve integrated AI into a project from initial prompt to final, polished design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Points:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic motion graphics or video editing skills (&lt;strong&gt;After Effects&lt;/strong&gt; or &lt;strong&gt;Premiere Pro&lt;/strong&gt;).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with the ethical and copyright considerations of AI-generated art.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Whole Person Promise:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Bandwidth, we’re pretty proud of our corporate culture, which is rooted in our “Whole Person Promise.” We promise all employees that they can have meaningful work AND a full life, and we provide a work environment geared toward enriching your body, mind, and spirit. How do we do that? Well…&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you ready for an awesome internship experience? At Bandwidth we’re all about making your time with us fun and fulfilling! Take a break with our 90-minute workout lunch to energize your day, or roll up your sleeves for some cool volunteer activities that give back to our community. You&#39;ll also get to meet and connect with our leaders who can share their wisdom and advice. And let’s not forget the fun social activities to bond with your fellow interns!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us for a summer full of learning, laughter, and new experiences—let’s make some great memories together!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you excited about the position and its responsibilities, but not sure if you’re 100% qualified? Do you feel you can work to help us crush the mission? If you answered ‘yes’ to both of these questions, we encourage you to apply! You won’t want to miss the opportunity to be a part of the BAND.&lt;/p&gt;
